## 🏁 VERDICT

iDesk adalah **functional internal tool** yang working, tapi BUKAN enterprise-grade software.

**Yang sudah baik:** Arsitektur modular, auth security, real-time updates, design token system, code splitting, SLA tracking.

**Yang kritis:** Zero meaningful test coverage, mass assignment vulnerability, race conditions pada ticket numbering, Docker build yang swallow errors, dan single page file 921 baris.

**Score 56/100** karena:
- Functional? Ya. Works? Ya.  
- Reliable? Tidak bisa dijamin tanpa tests.  
- Secure? Ada gaps critical (mass assignment, no input sanitization).  
- Scalable? Dashboard akan crash di 10k+ tickets.  
- Maintainable? God objects dan DRY violations everywhere.  

> iDesk butuh **3-4 sprint stabilization** sebelum layak disebut production-grade. Focus: P0 fixes → test coverage → DB normalization → CI/CD.
